akht un tsvantsikstn, nayn un tsvantsikstn shul-yor,

415
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:43,510
bin ikh zikh avek lernen in der Sofye Gurevitsh-gimnazye,

416
00:25:43,665 --> 00:25:46,520
velkhe hot zikh gefunen oyf Makove finf.

417
00:25:47,092 --> 00:25:48,848
di gimnazye iz nokh dan,

418
00:25:48,981 --> 00:25:51,250
ven ikh bin dan nokh ongekumen,

419
00:25:51,250 --> 00:25:54,730
iz nokh geven di farvalterin undzere,

420
00:25:54,730 --> 00:25:56,870
Sofye Markovne Gurevitsh.

421
00:25:56,870 --> 00:25:59,890
dos iz geven a oysergeveynlekher pedagog,

422
00:26:00,203 --> 00:26:02,759
di shul iz geven a private,

423
00:26:02,759 --> 00:26:07,781
un di lerer velkhe hobn bay undz gearbet in der shul,

424
00:26:07,811 --> 00:26:10,478
der, oyb nemen

425
00:26:10,478 --> 00:26:14,189
nor di reshime fun di lerer, bay undz hot gearbet

426
00:26:14,233 --> 00:26:18,240
di froy fun dokter Shabad, Stefanye Lvovne.

427
00:26:18,450 --> 00:26:19,989
bay undz hot gearbet

428
00:26:20,011 --> 00:26:21,833
di tokhter

429
00:26:21,833 --> 00:26:24,300
fun d- dokter Shabad,

430
00:26:24,322 --> 00:26:26,033
Regine Vaynraykh,

431
00:26:26,056 --> 00:26:30,060
di froy fun dem bavustn Va- Vaynraykh.

432
00:26:30,060 --> 00:26:31,771
bay undz hot gearbet,

433
00:26:31,771 --> 00:26:34,551
mayn ershte lererin iz geven

434
00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:37,810
Malke Khaimson.

435
00:26:37,810 --> 00:26:40,793
Khaimson, dos iz di froy fun Bastomski,

436
00:26:40,793 --> 00:26:43,815
velkhe hobn aroysgegebn di barimte

437
00:26:43,815 --> 00:26:47,860
kinder- -zhurnaln, "Di Grininke Beymelekh",

438
00:26:47,860 --> 00:26:50,771
un aroysgegebn dem "Khaver".

439
00:26:51,418 --> 00:26:52,996
dos zaynen geven undzere lerer.

440
00:26:53,107 --> 00:26:56,870
zeyer, s'iz geven nokh a sakh azoyne lerer. der lerer Rabinovitsh,

441
00:26:57,463 --> 00:27:00,490
vu s'iz bay undz geven a shul

442
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:04,810
velkhe ven ikh hob nakher shoyn gearbet in shul,

443
00:27:04,810 --> 00:27:06,907
ven nakher ven, dos iz geven,

444
00:27:06,907 --> 00:27:10,218
velkhe hot undz gegebn a oysergeveynlekhe ertsiung.

445
00:27:10,218 --> 00:27:12,841
un dos iz bay undz geblibn

446
00:27:12,841 --> 00:27:15,729
in, bay un- in di blutn, vi me zogt dos.

447
00:27:15,729 --> 00:27:18,774
kh'el aykh gebn aza min bayshpil. me hot undz,

448
00:27:18,774 --> 00:27:22,352
mir hobn ge-, mir esn kez, mir esn puter,

449
00:27:22,352 --> 00:27:23,732
mir ve-, veys nit v-,

450
00:27:23,732 --> 00:27:27,298
di lererin hot bashtelt spetsyel

451
00:27:27,298 --> 00:27:29,798
bay undzer a foter...

